title: Breaking News: SAB TV to come up with two new shows!
text: Tweet Optimystix Entertainment and Edit II to roll out their new shows on SAB TV! Check out here... As we had exclusively reported earlier about SAB TV to get revamped, We now bring to you the latest development update from the family entertainment channel. SAB TV is about to introduce Two new shows! Our reliable source informs, "SAB TV will soon have two new shows coming up by two Ace production houses. One of which is Optimystix Entertainment house that is bringing a comical show on the lines of famous show Yes Boss.""Another show is by Edit II, the makers of hilarious shows F.I.R. and Bhabhiji Ghar Par Hain? This show will have a Hospital background and the story will revolve around patients and doctors. Both these shows will be telecasted between 10 Pm to 11 Pm replacing Hum Aapke Ghar Mein Rehte Hai and Yam Hain Hum," reveals the source. We tried contacting the producer, Vipul D. Shah (Optimystix Entertainment) but failed to get any revert. Whereas, all our efforts to reach the producer, Sanjoy Kohli (Edit II Productions) went futile. For more exclusive news like this, stay tuned..
